caption.text: Experience a music night like never before as it collides with arts, fashion and F&B. Only at @fuse.2016 presented by BIMUS (BINUS International Music Society) on Nov 11, 2016 at Kuningan City Ballroom. Grab your tickets now on www.fuse-2016.com and don't miss it!

After a long wait, we present you our 12th lineup !

Maliq & D'Essentials is a well-known jazz and soul music based band who had their popularity incredibly increased especially among young people since their appearance in the Jakarta International Java Jazz Festival in 2005.

Named as The Best Album 2013 by Rolling Stone Indonesia for Sriwedari, no need to doubt the absolute quality of the distinctive music that the band holds.

The band which name stands for Music And Live Instrument Quality has performed in so many big cities yet concerts, and has proudly held their international showcase called Maliq & D'Essentials Live in Singapore 2013 at The Home Club, Singapore. Everyone, please welcome Maliq & D뗀ssentials.
